---
title: Cheesy Beef Mince Ragu Stew with Mushrooms and Ciabatta Dippers
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Cheesy Beef Mince Ragu Stew in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R09_W45_UK_R16134-3_Main__5low-f38fb1a1.jpg
